XML
    - create a file "phpunit.xml"; the shortest possible example is:
    
        <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?>
        <phpunit></phpunit>
        
ADD COLORS
    colors="true"
FILE TO EXECUTE BEFORE TESTS
    bootstrap="path/my-bootstrap-or-autoload-file.php"
MORE VERBOSITY
    verbose="true"
